Application Description:

ChefGenie is an online ordering app for unmanned retail devices. This includes receiving meal orders, booking meal orders, coupons, gift cards, order progress inquiries, and meal pickup notifications.



Function Introduction:

1. Online ordering: The user card can select a nearby location, select the corresponding product or package to place an order, and after payment, the order will be sent to the unmanned frying device at the location for frying.

2. Appointment for meal ordering: Users can choose their own suitable time to pick up meals, and can pick up meals at a certain time period in the next 12 hours.

3. Coupons: ChefGenie often sends coupons and gift cards for unmanned retail locations. After receiving, the order amount can be deducted.

4. Order progress query: On the app, you can check the progress of product preparation on the point device at any time and arrange the time for meal pickup based on the progress.

5. Dining notification: Obtain notification of the order's start and completion of cooking through the app's message.

Yindii is a surplus food app to rescue delicious unsold food from restaurants, cafes and grocery stores at 50% to 80% discount! Perfect for tonight's dinner or tomorrow's lunch!

Buy delicious unsold surplus food. Reserve and pay in the app. Take away or get delivered during happy hour. You will get a surprise box like it’s your birthday!



- Save Money

Find amazing happy hours in Bangkok in a variety of eco-friendly places and brands. An amazing way to discover new food and cool stores!




- Save the Planet

Be part of a global movement to reduce human impact on the planet and eradicate food waste by rescuing food that is too good to go.
